General.Name: Timbercreek Financial Corp
General.Description: Timbercreek Financial Corp., a mortgage investment company, provides shorter-duration structured financing solutions to commercial real estate investors in Canada. It focuses on lending against income-producing real estate properties, such as multi-residential, retail, and office properties in urban markets. The company was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
